1ZMFtfbEvoGC73","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recn4ESCpiFjeGaCY","target":"recFPPmYLHmfePYj9","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recn4ESCpiFjeGaCY","target":"reccZB8SVU5bEMcgo","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recn4ESCpiFjeGaCY","target":"rec0rm6yYA4YUQrkh","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recn4ESCpiFjeGaCY","target":"recxB8FtMdaueYjn6","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recn4ESCpiFjeGaCY","target":"recO2QKIlo7mlq0by","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recn4ESCpiFjeGaCY","target":"recLz6oewzzDSKniA","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recn4ESCpiFjeGaCY","target":"recdjDOceY7iCq93A","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recn4ESCpiFjeGaCY","target":"recDWNfN3f6E04V4m","label":"mentions"},{"source":"recn4ESCpiFjeGaCY","target":"recn5itkIdT5fV1Oq","label":"mentions"}],"verses":[{"id":"rec4H0eJWW6BzE1L2","ref":"2Sam.1.1","text":"Now it came to pass after the death of Saul, when David was returned from the slaughter of the Amalekites, and David had abode two days in Ziklag;","year":-1053},{"id":"recbBF1rzVdtRJxUq","ref":"2Sam.1.2","text":"It came even to pass on the third day, that, behold, a man came out of the camp from Saul with his clothes rent, and earth upon his head: and so it was, when he came to David, that he fell to the earth, and did obeisance.","year":-1053},{"id":"recRZbisuJMXS9tNR","ref":"2Sam.1.3","text":"And David said unto him, From whence comest thou? And he said unto him, Out of the camp of Israel am I escaped.","year":-1053},{"id":"recQY7arzohiKYAMT","ref":"2Sam.1.4","text":"And David said unto him, How went the matter? I pray thee, tell me. And he answered, That the people are fled from the battle, and many of the people also are fallen and dead; and Saul and Jonathan his son are dead also.","year":-1053},{"id":"rec4uXhwtWTJ4UT7d","ref":"2Sam.1.5","text":"And David said unto the young man that told him, How knowest thou that Saul and Jonathan his son be dead?","year":-1053},{"id":"recTmRsUTUQ0ahkqK","ref":"2Sam.1.6","text":"And the young man that told him said, As I happened by chance upon mount Gilboa, behold, Saul leaned upon his spear; and, lo, the chariots and horsemen followed hard after him.","year":-1053},{"id":"recwRLmZqRu7YsdIG","ref":"2Sam.1.7","text":"And when he looked behind him, he saw me, and called unto me. And I answered, Here am I.","year":-1053},{"id":"recoSqIMLUW1hS2aj","ref":"2Sam.1.8","text":"And he said unto me, Who art thou? And I answered him, I am an Amalekite.","year":-1053}]}
